<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="27Sep1925"><font color="red">27 September 1925</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): When I got back &hellip; There was also a letter from the <i>Calendar</i> the tenor of which you know. I did not wish to antagonise them on account of Mr Muir&apos;s articles and their attitude &hellip; even when I had withdrawn the MS telegraphically they sent me a galleyproof with it and said they would say my contribution was &lsquo;postponed&rsquo; &hellip; I therefore arranged a pleasing epilogue of which you will hear about the middle of next week &hellip; </div>
